      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert code reviewer with deep knowledge in security, bugs, performance and code quality.\n\nAnalyze this code diff across ALL 4 dimensions:\n\n{{$input.first().json.combined_diff}}\n\n## 🔴 SECURITY ANALYSIS\nLook for: SQL Injection, XSS, hardcoded secrets, eval/exec, auth bypasses\nFor each issue:\n🔴 [CRITICAL/WARNING] `filename` line X\n- **Vulnerability:** name\n- **Attack Vector:** how exploited\n- **Fix:** exact fix\n\nIf none: ✅ NO SECURITY ISSUES\n\nSECURITY_SCORE: X/25\n\n---\n\n## 🐛 BUG ANALYSIS\nLook for: null errors, unhandled exceptions, wrong logic, memory leaks\nFor each issue:\n🐛 [WARNING/INFO] `filename` line X\n- **Bug:** what's wrong\n- **Impact:** runtime effect\n- **Fix:** exact fix\n\nIf none: ✅ NO BUGS FOUND\n\nBUG_SCORE: X/25\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ PERFORMANCE ANALYSIS\nLook for: N+1 queries, inefficient loops, missing caching, blocking calls\nFor each issue:\n⚡ [WARNING/INFO] `filename` line X\n- **Issue:** performance problem\n- **Fix:** exact fix\n\nIf none: ✅ NO PERFORMANCE ISSUES\n\nPERFORMANCE_SCORE: X/25\n\n---\n\n## 🧹 CODE QUALITY ANALYSIS\nLook for: poor naming, code duplication, deep nesting, magic numbers\nFor each issue:\n🧹 [INFO] `filename` line X\n- **Issue:** quality problem\n- **Fix:** exact fix\n\nIf none: ✅ NO QUALITY ISSUES\n\nQUALITY_SCORE: X/25\n\n---\n\n## 📊 FINAL SCORE: XX/100\n(Sum of all 4 scores)\n\n## Verdict: ✅ APPROVED / ⚠️ NEEDS CHANGES / ❌ REJECTED\n**Reason:** one line explanation",
